Book covers (docs/seed/covers/, docs/screenshots/, website/public/shots/)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

The book covers shown in screenshots, marketing materials, and the
showcase seed dataset remain the property of their respective publishers
and rights-holders. They are reproduced here, at thumbnail resolution,
solely to illustrate the Tome application — they are not redistributed
as standalone artwork, and their inclusion is consistent with the
standard practice across self-hosted ebook software (Calibre-Web,
Komga, Kavita, Audiobookshelf, etc.).

If you are a rights-holder and would like a specific cover removed,
open an issue at https://github.com/bndct-devops/tome/issues and we
will swap it.

Sources used for cover acquisition:
  - Hardcover (https://hardcover.app)            — most novel and manga covers
  - Open Library (https://openlibrary.org)       — backup novel covers
  - Wikimedia Commons (https://commons.wikimedia.org) — comic first-issues
  - The maintainer's own Tome instance covers     — for series we already had


