KOReader plugin protocol (backend/api/kosync.py)
------------------------------------------------

Tome implements compatibility with the KOReader sync protocol (KOSync).
The protocol itself is documented at:
  https://github.com/koreader/koreader-sync-server

Tome ships no KOReader code; the KOReader plugin is licensed AGPL-3.0
(same as Tome) and developed independently.


